Maxima made her way to the CR Chamber. Not able to locate Blackstorm. 
However, despite how wounded & terribly weak she was, Maxima looked at the Clone of 
Blackstorm in the secured chamber. 

Then, she stumbled over to a CR & submersed herself in it's basking warmth of 
energy & repairs. As she rested, she awaited Hydras.
